<h1 id="-remove-primary-key-">*.remove( <code>primary key</code> )</h1>
<h3 id="purpose" permalink="purpose">Purpose</h3>
<p>Used to remove records from the join table that is automatically generated during a many-to-many association. Unlike .add(), it only accepts the primary key of the model instance (defaults to record ID).</p>
<h3 id="overview" permalink="overview">Overview</h3>
