<h3 id="notes" permalink="notes">Notes</h3>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>Any string arguments passed must be the primary key of the record.</li>
<li><code>.remove()</code> alone won&apos;t actually persist the change in associations to the databse.  You should call <code>.save()</code> after using <code>.add()</code> or <code>.remove()</code>.</li>
</ul>
